				</ORIGINAL-REFEX>
			</REFERENCE>
			<STRING> has erupted many times since and  </STRING>
			<REFERENCE ID="9" SEMCAT="mountain" SYNCAT="np-subj">
				<ORIGINAL-REFEX>
					<REFEX CASE="" EMPHATIC="" HEAD="" TYPE="empty">_</REFEX>
				</ORIGINAL-REFEX>
			</REFERENCE>
			<STRING> is today regarded as one of the most dangerous volcanoes in the world because of the population of 3,000,000 people now living close to  </STRING>
